title: Yahoo Lifestyle
text: Cultivating prime time with family and friends recharges your batteries and strengthens loosening bonds. You might be fresh out of motivation necessary to handle the simplest of responses and concerns. If youre feeling drained today, you could try to cover your vulnerability with anger rather than with acceptance. But fighting unnecessary battles will quickly sap your energy. Fortunately, you can relax and surrender with people who love you unconditionally, trusting they have your back like you have theirs. Love revitalizes every cell in your body.
